  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\"><img alt=\"House Wode.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/50px-House_Wode.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/75px-House_Wode.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/100px-House_Wode.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Oswald Wode</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\"><img alt=\"House Wode.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/50px-House_Wode.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/75px-House_Wode.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/100px-House_Wode.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\">House Wode</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Oswald Wode</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\">House Wode</a> and a supporter of the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oswald_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond%27s_march_on_Harrenhal\" title=\"Aemond&#39;s march on Harrenhal\">marched</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> toward <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>, his <a href=\"/index.php/Vanguard\" title=\"Vanguard\">vanguard</a> defeated Oswald, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Darry_(Dance)\" title=\"Lord Darry (Dance)\">Lord Darry</a>, and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Roote\" title=\"House Roote\">Roote</a> in a short and sharp battle on the eastern shore of the <a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye\" title=\"Gods Eye\">Gods Eye</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oswald_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404092256\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.129 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.764 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 438/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10433/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5287/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 461/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 715/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.320/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  746.302      1 -total\n 97.75%  729.514      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.35%  726.551      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.97%   81.885     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.74%   35.377      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.12%    8.328      1 Template:Ref\n  0.81%    6.012      1 Template:Date\n  0.79%    5.891      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.28%    2.058      1 Template:References\n  0.18%    1.320      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcac